[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "入夜，世界树公司档案室。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "档案室里配备了用于检索资料的大型终端，它们几乎储存着公司——乃至整个世界的知识和秘密，并严格按照权限提供给不同的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而从傍晚开始，最深处那间阅览室的灯就一直亮着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "薇蒂雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "薇蒂雅站在门外，正犹豫着要不要敲开这扇门，而就在这时，门忽然唰地朝内被拉开了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "薇蒂雅？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "薇蒂雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员大人……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们同时出声，又同时沉默下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "呃……要不，进来说？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我侧过身子，给薇蒂雅让出了一条路，她则快速点了点头，踏着小碎步走了进来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我使用的终端屏幕仍然亮着，不用说，薇蒂雅一进门便看到了屏幕上的内容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "薇蒂雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这些……都是卜卜的档案？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，从出生到现在，我能找到的所有信息，都在这里了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有人工智能帮忙整理，倒是没花多少时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我注视着屏幕上密密麻麻的文件，只觉得它们正逐渐拼凑出一个模糊的面庞。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "非说自己是什么天师，结果完全没接受过这方面的教学，连铜钱都是买的公司的仿制品。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "成绩普通，体能也不好，教师评价上却都写着“阳光开朗，乐于助人”，根本就是个幻想自己是侠客的笨蛋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "加入公司也是，就因为在降临事件中当了一段时间志愿者，就稀里糊涂成了外勤干员……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "薇蒂雅",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员大人……为什么要收集这些信息？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "硬要说的话……我现在才想起来找这些信息才没道理吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她突然出现，改变了我的所有计划，我也凭着内心的想法决定去救她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但这么多天以来，我除了她的名字和职务，实际上对她一无所知。就在这样的情况下，我还答应了要带她做神经调理……哈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我深吸了口气，又一点一点将之吐出。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在，有了这些资料和这些天以来的相处，我终于真正感觉能救回她了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以不用担心我，薇蒂雅，关键时刻，我会拽紧你给我的丝线的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我摊开手掌，看向右手无名指上萦绕着的紫色丝线。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接下来，我就要全力以赴了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "再次躺进治疗舱时，我只感觉到出乎意料的平静。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我的脑中，过往的每一次经历形成了彼此交汇的路径，通往终点的长卷也随之徐徐展开。而好消息是，这些道路的可优化空间还很多。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "情报，便是我现在最有价值的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只需要在某一段直道上加快些步伐，又在某一个岔口前抄上一条近路，就能得到宝贵的时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而这些时间，能够去做更多事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是我，卜卜。我们终于见面了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "至于这个手铐……其实是公司最新研发的天启者力量激发器。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-3",
        "Flag": "b-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "b-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我觉得，这三条路都不太好走的样子。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-4",
        "Flag": "b-4",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "b-4-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还真是充满故事性的经历啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "踏着我为自己铺好的道路，我们终于再一次来到了那棵巨树下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但还不能停在这里。这里太开阔，虽然正面战斗比较有利，但并不适合伏击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "时间……应该也还来得及。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你快看那边！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，真是一棵大树啊。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对了，在这里，还有一个约定要给她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好了卜卜，比起出去以后的事情，接下来我需要你先帮我一些忙。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "将拉勾的手松开后，我的表情重新变得严肃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯？要做什么？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们要想办法，伏击那个邪祟。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "伏、伏击？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不可能……我是说，想要战胜那东西，应该很难……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜的脸上出现了少有的惊恐，那怪物毕竟源于她心中的恐惧，就算只是提到也会让她下意识感到慌张。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "正因为这样，伏击才是唯一可行的办法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我会为你创造出足够的时间，在这段时间内，你需要尽可能对它造成伤害，只有你才能做到这件事。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我知道，你对自己没有信心，但我希望你相信我，这是我一路上都在思考的方法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我明白了……原来分析员这一路上都在思考着战斗，不愧是分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是啊……真是足够长的一段路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看向巨树前方狭长的通道，朝卜卜点了点头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总之，我们先前进吧，得先找个好地方才行。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在哪？到底在哪？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它只觉得自己心中有一团火，而这火焰已经快要将它自己燃烧殆尽。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "沿途抓到的那些小东西都太弱了，它们甚至都来不及攻击，就都被它的爪子拍碎。如此往复几次，它心中的火便愈发灼痛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那猎物究竟在哪？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它能感觉到猎物的气息，但在这迷宫般的地下洞窟中，它怎么也找不到对方的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有几次，它分明感觉猎物已经近在眼前。但稍一恍惚，对方又消失了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它已经忍耐到了极限，所以这一次，当它又一次感觉到猎物就在不远处时，它第一时间便用利爪划开了自己的手臂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "剧痛令它爆发出前所未有的速度，一个拐角，两个拐角……它庞大的身躯穿行在洞窟之中，却诡异地没有发出任何声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "终于，它闻到猎物的气味了。猎物就在前面，就在那块石头后面——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它扑了上去，爪尖划破空气，划破了猎物的衣服。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……但是，也只有衣服，一套世界树公司分析员专属的制服外套。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它随即感觉到了危机，而就在这时，一颗小小的子弹朝它飞来，却并未击中它的头颅，而是打中了它的脚下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它还来不及庆幸，便被一阵又一阵的爆炸掀翻在地。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果它有人类的智慧，应该会意识到自己脚下被埋满了爆炸物，只等待着一颗子弹将其引爆。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果它更聪明一些，或许还能猜到，这是从矿洞深处的武器库里找到的，由世界树公司生产的炸药，威力一向十分惊人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "动手！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 73,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "实际上无需我的命令，在怪物失衡的同时，卜卜已经心领神会地发起了攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 74,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "密集的子弹穿进爆炸产生的硝烟中，难以确认是否命中。但无论是我还是卜卜，都是只是重复着射击和装弹的动作。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 75,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "直至爆炸逐渐停止，硝烟中也不再传出声音。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 76,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "它……死了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 77,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不，我心中的危机感并没有完全消失。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 78,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "下一刻，眼前不过几道残影闪过，全身皮开肉绽的怪物便已经突进到了我的面前。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 79,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "来不及言语，我只能凭着直觉将身边的卜卜推开。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 80,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一阵寒光闪过，有那么一瞬间，我已经感觉到右臂传出了幻痛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 81,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但那锋利的兽爪最终准确地落在了我所想的位置——我和卜卜的正中间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 82,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "巨大的力量立刻将那手铐的链条，连同链条之下的地面一同劈断，发出震耳欲聋的巨响。我和卜卜则因为分开时的力度，一左一右飞了出去，在地面上翻滚了几圈才停下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 83,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "该死的，这东西到底……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 84,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我听到卜卜痛骂了一句，紧接着又开了几枪还击。但这些子弹也像之前的一样，如同投入了大海的石子，激不起任何波澜。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 85,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不过，她的攻击的确吸引了怪物的注意，它立刻朝着卜卜扑去，却也将后背完全暴露给了我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 86,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "此时，已经来不及思考手铐断开后意识连接会不会受到影响，我心中一动，随即箭步上前，用手臂死死扼住了怪物的脖颈。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 87,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "跑！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 88,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "赶在怪物反抗之前，我只能对卜卜下达最简单直接的命令。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 89,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在这样狭小的空间中战斗，我们很难应对它的攻击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 90,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样一来，唯一的办法就是近身牵制住怪物，给卜卜创造出拉开距离射击的机会。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 91,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然，如果她直接逃走，也不是什么坏事。虽然仅凭我一己之力很难战胜眼前的怪物，但想逃脱战斗也并不困难……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 92,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我……才不会跑！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 93,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可卜卜似乎没有理解我的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 94,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她非但没有逃开，反而稳住了身形，趁着怪物试图把我甩下的时机，势大力沉地朝怪物的腹部挥出了一拳。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 95,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "接——招！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 96,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "砰！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 97,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我完全没想到她会来这么一手，只能眼睁睁看着怪物的腹部如漏气般肉眼可见地凹陷下去，随即连带着我一起仰面倒下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 98,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在即将与地面亲密接触的前一刻，我一个翻滚，堪堪躲过了怪物身体的重击。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 99,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不是吧！这都还能动弹！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 100,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没等我缓过神，一只手便伸了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 101,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在，是该跑了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 102,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "往哪里跑，这是一个问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 103,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然不可能原路返回，那段路崎岖难行，还有河流阻隔，最重要的是，根本没有出去的路。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 104,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "现在，我们只能继续向前，赌这条向上的路最终通向的是一个适合战斗的地方。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 105,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "用拳头去应对这种怪物，真亏你能想得出来……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 106,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们之间明明已经没有了手铐的束缚，却仍然保持着相反的步调。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 107,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谁让你当时让我先跑！我一生气……就想揍它！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 108,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我是让你先拉开距离，你是笨蛋吗！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 109,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我一边骂着，却又忍不住笑了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 110,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "笨蛋就笨蛋吧！本天师干过的聪明事多了去了……多的是能抵消的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 111,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没跑多远，眼前的洞穴慢慢亮了起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 112,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我也终于看清，卜卜正紧紧用左手抓着自己的右手腕，而她的右手已经明显肿胀起来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 113,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别看了，骨折了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 114,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "即使在全速奔跑中，她也一如既往地对我的目光做出了反应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 115,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那玩意的身体简直是铁打的……不过没关系，我两只手都是惯用手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 116,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她呲牙咧嘴地擦了擦额头的汗，又下意识看向我的手。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 117,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你的手又是怎么回事，怎么看上去也肿起来了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 118,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我这是……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 119,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "话语尚未出口便被身后传来怒吼声打断。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 120,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但与此同时，卜卜带着惊喜的喊声又将我的意识拽了回来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 121,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出口！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 122,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不远处，刺眼的光芒正从前方的洞口中照进这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 123,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我们顿时卯足了最后的力气，像是在沙漠中看到了绿洲的旅人一样，冲进了洞口之中。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 124,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "然而——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "出现在眼前的，只不过是一个更大的洞窟。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "光线从洞窟顶部的空隙中刺入，将这里照得亮堂堂，也给予了我们虚假的希望。而现在，我们不得不面对现实。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "无路可逃了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 128,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但在那怪物追过来之前，还有事情要做。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 129,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "把断了的那只手给我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 130,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 131,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然一头雾水，卜卜还是把右手伸了过来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 132,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "待会优先自保，别和那东西硬碰硬。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 133,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一边说着，我忽然一拳打向身边的岩壁，几片岩石碎片立刻掉落下来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 134,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "等等！现在也不是泄愤的时候吧！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 135,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只是把你干过的傻事再干一遍罢了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 136,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我没有理会目瞪口呆的卜卜，只是从地上的石片中挑了相对平整的一块，又扯下身上的衣服，撕成了长长的布条。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 137,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我来吸引它的注意，你负责提供火力掩护，打几枪转移一下位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 138,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我将石片贴在她的手腕上，又用布条将她的右手和石片固定住，做成了一个简易的夹板。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 139,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好了，不乱动应该就没问题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 140,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "卜卜，只靠我一个人一定无法战胜那个怪物，但我们两个人就可以。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 141,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以这次，不是你保护我或者我保护你，我们，要一起去战胜它。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 142,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我朝她伸出手，而她毫不犹豫地将手放了上来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 143,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卜卜",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯！我们一起上吧，分析员！",
        "disable": 0
    }
]